Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estou de volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Benvida. {good song}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chegouche un paquete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que mercaches?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:17.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unha dakimakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:22.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quero dicir... algo que atopei en liña que alivia o estrés.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Se funciona, dimo. {Yeah. Tired. Right.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Claro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non podo contarllo... {even though it's going on your bed?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa vexo...  de verdade é Samaín.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ides conseguir clientes con isto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamén estamos facendo un evento para o primeiro día.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Evento?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:03.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Imos convidar ós nenos do barrio e amosarlles como facer doces e repartilos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:06.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Os traballadores van estar vestidos coma monstros.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:07.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estou de volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:10.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Queres dicilos teus avós?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:14.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O resto da familia tamén.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Entón axudarei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:17.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que pasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avó!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:22.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avó, estás ben??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:23.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Está frío!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:29.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chama unha ambulancia, Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vale!! {yeah, let's just toss the possible corpse around}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avó...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, é Kyou-chan. Benvido!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avó!! O avó...{FOTC: Consistency: Gramps or Grandpa?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estase facendo o morto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:50.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non espera, de verdade está morto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O seu corpo xa está frío!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:56.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fai un anaco entrou na neveira da tenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Así que foi por iso...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pero non ten pulso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,El sempre tivo o pulso feble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Por que cheira a cadáver? {why do you know what a corpse smells like?}{Obviously someone made a pass at Manami.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:12.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ese é o seu cheiro natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pero... espera...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:23.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avó, se non paras, vouche arranca-los pelos da cabeza un a un.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:31.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, es un demo de muller.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:34.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Como poderías pensar en danar o pouco pelo que me queda?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ves?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:40.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Feliz Samaín, Kyou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Truco ou... que ía despois?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Comezou a apodrece-lo teu cerebro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:47.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal é o número da ambulancia??
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Coma se o soubera!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alégrome moito de que sigas vivo, avó!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, perdoa por iso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:00.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Deixeime levar un pouco...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quero golpearche na cara!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que pasa, Kyou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Por que facialo morto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:12.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estaba practicando o meu disfraz para mañá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:14.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A miña actuación de zombie foi impresionante, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,En realidade, parecías máis un cadáver normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:21.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calquera neno que te vexa quedará traumatizado.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:23.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non creo que deberas deixarlles ver iso.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten razón, sabes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É certo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:33.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pois ben entón.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:36.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non é coma se me importase
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non te molestes consolandoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:42.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Se xogas con el, volverá a pasarse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Entón vou buscar uns doces de Samaín.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Irei axudala.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:55.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Parece que es popular coas avoíñas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iso non me fai feliz!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Por que estaba iso en plural?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:01.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa o fixechedes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:02.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Face-lo que!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:03.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,E claro que non o fixemos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe, é An-chan! Fai un tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ola, fai tempo—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:09.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que che pasou no pelo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Curteino todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:12.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que opinas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:14.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Os rapados son populares hoxe en día!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ese é un corte de monxe, xa sabes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ningún rapado vese así.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non hai xeito, An-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:28.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O perruqueiro dixo: "Certo, rapado. rapado". despois curtouno coa súa maquina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:31.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Incluso preguntou que tan curto o quería.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É un peiteado completamente diferente.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:35.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Deberías usar unha navalla especial para iso.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:36.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non é que eu saiba moito sobre iso...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:37.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non hai xeito!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ese perruqueiro mentiume!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa me parecía!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:45.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Desde que volveches con iso teño ganas de dicir
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non hai "rapado" aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:47.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,por moito tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Deberías terllo dito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:56.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Curtache-lo pelo por un capricho así que estache ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Parvo Rock! {is this what it's supposed to be?}{FOTC: Yeah.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rock"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe, toma isto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:03.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cando volveu do perruqueiro estaba todo coma
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:09.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mira o meu peiteado incrible! A partir de agora podes chamarme Rock!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O teu nome é Iwao...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamura Iwao...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tódolos adultos son uns mentireiros! {Some good angst there.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non te fíes deses maiores de 50! {That's a good one.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iso é moi elaborado...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:27.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:36.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Por favor proba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Claro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:51.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É xenial!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,En serio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:55.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poñeches cabaza de verdade dentro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si! Notase?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fíxechelos ti?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Por que?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, querías sabe-lo que penso...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:07.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si, fixenos...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alégrome moito de que che gusten!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:13.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:17.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Por que non casades xa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avó!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:23.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ás veces mesmo ten sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:26.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, parade volos dous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, vamos á miña habitación.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Claro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:36.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guau! Estase poñendo quente aló!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iso é tan vello...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:38.61,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, en serio?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:10:57.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Espera aquí un segundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estás agochando algo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:00.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si, supoño que non é {\i1}ela{\i0} da que estamos falando.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que foi iso?{Kirino yandere end too?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:25.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabíao! {like she'd buy a non ero one...}{This is why I don't open the package.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non cambiou bocado...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Para de ollar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:43.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É vergoñento...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... que deberiamos facer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Durme.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Creo que me quedei ata tarde estudando demasiado estes días.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:02.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Teño ganas de relaxarme e botar unha sesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:02.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Está ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Entón iso é o que querías dicir...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non se permite estudar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesmo deixei os meus libros na escols.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:10.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa vexo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Só relaxemonos entón.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Traerei un pouco de té.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:15.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:28.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non necesitas axudar a prepara-la feira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:31.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si, pero iso será despois de que peche a tenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A familia enteira vai estar traballando niso
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Botarei unha man entón.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:36.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,En serio?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sería unha gran axuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non estades cansos?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Está ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:44.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non te preocupes por min.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moitisimas grazas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:49.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non é exactamente un pago, pero podes cear aquí entón.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira, un talo de té está en pé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:54.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe, xenial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:06.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Compraches un dakimakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:08.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Realmente non tes intención de parar, non?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:12.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!? Traballei moi duro para mercañas miñas cousas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:15.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ademais, unha almofada é unha necesidade cotiá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:17.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non tes dereito a dicirmo que facer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non é realmente unha necesidade, non si?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:21.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É só para satisfacer un engano para esa neniña.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non é unha neniña!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Meru-chan é unha rapaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,UNHA MOZA MÁ-XIC-A..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:27.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vale, vale. Acouga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:32.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,De calquera xeito, Kiririn-san, cal foi a reacción do teu irmán Kyousuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:37.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pensei que o deixarías mirar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:39.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pero aínda non chegou a casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:42.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,sempre que o necesitas, nunca está por aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:46.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Probablemente sentiu o aura de súcubo na casa e temía pola súa vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non o enmeiguei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:52.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Creo que foi á biblioteca con aquela moza sinxela.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Da que sempre esta falando.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:56.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non é que realmente me importe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:59.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A Onii-sama gustanlle ese tipo de mozas?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:01.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estou abraiada. Non o parecía.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Nunca cho dixo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:05.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Escoitoo por primeira vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Así que, como é?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:11.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É unha amiga da infancia, leva anteollos, e é parva.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que demo? Estiveches agochando un lote.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:16.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Contanos todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa vexo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:21.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Almorzas tóolos días con el, polo que é obvio que sabes máis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non entendo realmente a súa relación
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,pero todo sobre ela é...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,sinxelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guau, isto é pesado!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, grazas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que demo estás facendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:56.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan, agora entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O Rock non é a túa apariencia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:14:59.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É un xeito de vivir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:03.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai pouca diferenza entre ir rapado e un corte curto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:05.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mañá, berro con toda a miña alma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,E por que estás tocando un shamisen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:10.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iso é máis coma un músico biwa ca un roqueiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non temos unha guitarra—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:16.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Axuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:17.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Home, estou canso.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:29.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bo traballo, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:33.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... queres cear ou bañarte primeiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bañarse?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:42.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai tempo que non nos visitaches, así que o avó, a avoa e papá dixeron que deberías quedar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:44.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, xa vexo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:51.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O avó, a avoa e papá están moi felices de verte de novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O avó—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O Avó e a avoa—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avo—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O avó díxolle a avoa—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:16:00.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Enténdoo, vou durmir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:02.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estás seguro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:03.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, si.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:04.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mañá é fin de semana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:12.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai moito tempo que non quedas durmires.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:13.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Supoño que tes razón.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:15.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamén antes viña todo o tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poida ser por que, sabes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:24.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Agora tes esa idade, así que te ponches nervioso quedando na casa dunha moza.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:27.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Por que me poñería nervioso quedando na túa casa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:28.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non te pos?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:30.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Claro que non.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:32.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É máis relaxante aquí que na miña casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que pasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:41.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nada, só pensei que podería ser mellor así.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onde está el?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:02.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Está quedando en cas Tamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestamente, sempre actuando coma un neno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Falaches cos pais?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Claro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:11.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dixo que axudou co Samaín.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.27,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Samaín?{Dad}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grazas pola comida. {Kirino}{FOTC: How do we do itadakimasu?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:13.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si.{Mom}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:18.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grazas pola comida.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:27.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan, como tocas un C menor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:30.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non hai acordes no shamisen, sabes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:34.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, papá está a piques de saír do baño. Queres ir seguinte?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:37.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Podo ir último. Vai ti primeiro.{And drink that delicious bathwater.}{http://fotc.ath.cx/images/121488582250.jpg} {why do you have that on hand....}{Because it's good.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:39.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estou ben indo atrás de túa.{And drink that delicious bathwater.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non, toma un primeiro{And drink that delicious bathwater.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:54.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Entón, que tal tomar un xuntos?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, estaste poñendo encarnado!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moi ben! Bañemonos xuntos!{Pro SFX}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:07.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,En serio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Súper en serio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa me convidaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:13.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non podes botarte atrás agora, non si?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:16.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan, es un verdadeiro home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seino, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maldición! Tan xenial!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vamos, Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:24.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amosareiche a miña hiper-arma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avó, que fago??
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:32.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan quere tomar un baño comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non vaias contarllo a todo o mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:35.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Entón, vai con el.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Qu—era unha broma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Así que tamén queres.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:40.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non quero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:52.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Parvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gracias polo baño.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:59.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cando queiras.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:02.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Puxen un futón na túa habitación de sempre.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grazas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Supoño que durmirei entón.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Volverei á miña habitación.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:09.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe, avoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ensiname coma tocar isto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:11.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Claro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:14.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que queres tocar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Algo de rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:19.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cantos anos hai desde que estivemos ata a hora de durmir xuntos?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Catro anos, creo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:27.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Boas noites.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:28.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan! Kyou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O meu futón...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:40.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? O meu futón?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aparentemente...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Po-Por que está aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,E xusto ó lado do teu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:48.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fíxeches isto, Kyou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:49.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nin de carallada!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:52.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Acouga, acouga...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:54.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Analiza a situación.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:56.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, así que basicamente... Fíxeno!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, calma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avó!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:02.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que estás facendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Só algo co meu corazón...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que demo estás facendo, avó!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:21.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É un trauma da guerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:26.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Se non durmes aí con Manami, o meu peito adoece coa dor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:28.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que clase de trauma causa iso!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:30.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a dor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:33.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A avoa está chamando por min dende o outro lado do río Estixe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:35.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A avoa está abaixo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isto é moi raro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non podemos durmir xuntos a nosa idade!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non creo que ela—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:41.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:44.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estou ben con iso...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Se estás dacordo con iso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:51.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pois aí o tedes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:53.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que!? Agarda, maldito tolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:13.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É coma se foramos nenos de novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:18.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Daquela durmiamos así todo o tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nunca pensei que o faríamos a esta idade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:23.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É todo culpa dese vello tolo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:25.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,E avoa... poida que outra vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:29.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vou durmir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Boas noites.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:33.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Boas noites, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aínda estás esperto?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:45.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aínda estou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:47.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:52.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sería xenial ir á mesma universidade
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:54.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:22:01.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pregúntome como serán as cousas se nos graduamos e imos á mesma facultade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:02.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Como sería?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:04.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:09.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non creo que cambie moito.{FOTC: I don't think they'll change much.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:12.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poida.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:15.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe, Manami...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:16.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:21.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que pasaría se alguén che dixera que lle gustas?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:22.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que farías?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:24.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Qu-Qu-Que?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:25.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"E se"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:27.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É hipotetico!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:31.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ese tipo de tipo fantástico pode que nunca apareza!{FOTC: It's not like that kind of messed up guy might never appear!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:36.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Se... non sei que se.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:39.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Imaxina...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.47,0:22:40.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perdoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:44.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:46.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Se alguén che dixese que lle gustas, que farías?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:54.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rexeitariao.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:56.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Por que?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:23:00.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gustaríame vivir unha vida pacifica.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:02.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As cousas están do xeito que están agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:06.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poder relaxarme neste tipo de casa é suficiente para min.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:09.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa vexo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:15.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aínda nos queda moito camiño por percorrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:17.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Falas coma unha verdadeira avoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:20.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, ti falas coma un avó.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:27.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:28.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poida que a vindeira vez...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:31.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:35.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perdoa... non importa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:36.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A vindeira vez...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:40.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Queres vir á miña casa a vindeira vez?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:43.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:47.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si, gustaríame.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:49.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Algunha vez pronto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:50.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vale.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.63,0:23:52.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Boas noites.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.30,0:23:54.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cantas veces van agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.17,0:23:55.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vou durmir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:04.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, non volvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.81,0:24:08.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Parvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:28.08,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,nagaku chikaku ni iru to mienakunaru mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:28.08,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Cando levas tanto tempo xuntos, ás veces esquéceste diso
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.40,0:24:34.46,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka dokoka de mitsukete watashi ha kawatta
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.40,0:24:34.46,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Algunha vez, nalgún lugar, atopeino, pero cambiara
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.46,0:24:40.09,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,nee anata ha kawaranai ne dakara modokashii no
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.46,0:24:40.09,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe, parece que nunca cambias, por iso estou tan molesta
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.43,0:24:47.10,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,demo tabun sou iu toko fukumete suki nanda
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.43,0:24:47.10,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Pero creo que iso é parte do que me gusta de ti
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.10,0:24:51.98,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mata futari de kaeteyuku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.10,0:24:51.98,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Nós seguimos medramdo xuntos
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.98,0:24:58.11,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto konna kankei ga tsudzukeba ii no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.98,0:24:58.11,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Aínda que sería tan agradable quedarse así para sempre
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.45,0:25:05.91,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,kyuu ni sunda kono maegami mitai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.45,0:25:05.91,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Igual que o meu flequillo que de súpeto cortei
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.91,0:25:11.54,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mezameta omoi ga mou modoranai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.91,0:25:11.54,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Os meus sentimentos xurdiron todos, agora non podo volver
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.92,0:25:18.38,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,jimi na watashi dakedo sono mama de ii
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.92,0:25:18.38,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Podería ser tan sinxelo, pero todo está ben
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.70,0:25:25.77,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,anata no kotoba atsuku atsuku nokotteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.70,0:25:25.77,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Todo o que dixeches aínda me quenta no fondo
